    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a super reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure, you've found it! This car has been a total gem for me\u2014it's in great shape, runs like a dream, and is honestly just a joy to drive. I've taken solid care of it, and it's looking for a new home where it can keep hitting the road. Come take a look, I'm sure you'll fall in love with it!",
