    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit is mechanically robust, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already completed and the high-pressure VANOS system recently overhauled. The S54\u2019s individual throttle bodies deliver exceptional throttle response, paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock. Preventative maintenance includes a recent rod bearing replacement and valve adjustment. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the chassis remains sharp thanks to upgraded polyurethane bushings and a well-sorted suspension geometry. This is a performance-oriented example optimized for mechanical longevity and tactile feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Title in hand. Ready for immediate use.",
