    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly such a gem! \ud83d\ude97 It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It\u2019s in solid shape and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
