      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. The dual-VANOS system has been meticulously maintained to preserve torque delivery across the rev range. Shifting is handled by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission paired with a Variable M Differential Lock for superior traction out of corners. The chassis is structurally sound with proactive subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut and multi-link suspension geometry remains true. While showing light signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity and throttle response are sharp, offering a pure, analog connection to the road.",
